content:
Resolve Transaction Disputes Faster with Prebuilt Mastercom Integration

Transaction Dispute Management now integrates with Mastercom to assist in resolving transaction disputes with an efficient chargeback process. Use this integration to protect customers against fraudulent or unsatisfactory transactions.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Professional, Enterprise, and Unlimited editions where Financial Services Cloud is enabled.

Who: Users need the OmniStudio Admin, OmniStudio User, and Financial Services Cloud Extension or FSC Service permission sets.

Why: A robust dispute resolution process for card transactions is essential to protect customers against unauthorized charges, unsatisfactory purchases, and errors. By integrating Transaction Dispute Management with Mastercom, streamline the chargeback initiation process to facilitate a reliable and transparent dispute resolution process.
title: Streamlining Chargeback Process with Mastercom Integration
